english":"to Our Verses","translit":"liāyātinā","root":"أيي","audio":"wbw/074_016_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَنِيدًۭا","english":"stubborn","translit":"ʿanīdan","root":"عند","audio":"wbw/074_016_006.mp3"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"I will cover him with arduous torment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَأُرْهِقُهُۥ","english":"Soon I will cover Him","translit":"sa-ur'hiquhu","root":"رهق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَعُودًا","english":"(with) a laborious punishment","translit":"ṣaʿūdan","root":"صعد"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Indeed, he thought and deliberated.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, he","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَكَّرَ","english":"thought","translit":"fakkara","root":"فكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَدَّرَ","english":"and plotted","translit":"waqaddara","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"So may he be destroyed [for] how he deliberated.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقُتِلَ","english":"So may he be destroyed","translit":"faqutila","root":"قتل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","english":"how","translit":"kayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَدَّرَ","english":"he plotted","translit":"qaddara","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Then may he be destroyed [for] how he deliberated.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قُتِلَ","english":"may he be destroyed","translit":"qutila","root":"قتل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","english":"how","translit":"kayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَدَّرَ","english":"he plotted","translit":"qaddara","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"Then he considered [again];","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَظَرَ","english":"he looked","translit":"naẓara","root":"نظر"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"Then he frowned and scowled;","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَبَسَ","english":"he frowned","translit":"ʿabasa","root":"عبس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَبَسَرَ","english":"and scowled","translit":"wabasara","root":"بسر"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Then he turned back and was arrogant","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْبَرَ","english":"he turned back","translit":"adbara","root":"دبر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱسْتَكْبَرَ","english":"and was proud","translit":"wa-is'takbara","root":"كبر"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And said, \"This is not but magic imitated [from others].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","english":"Then he said","translit":"faqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنْ","english":"Not","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَآ","english":"(is) this","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"سِحْرٌۭ","english":"magic","translit":"siḥ'run","root":"سحر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُؤْثَرُ","english":"imitated","translit":"yu'tharu","root":"أثر"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"This is not but the word of a human being.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنْ","english":"Not","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰذَآ","english":"(is) this","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَوْلُ","english":"(the) word","translit":"qawlu","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْبَشَرِ","english":"(of) a human being","translit":"l-bashari","root":"بشر"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"I will drive him into Saqar.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَأُصْلِيهِ","english":"Soon I will drive him","translit":"sa-uṣ'līhi","root":"صلي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَقَرَ","english":"(into) Hell","translit":"saqara","root":""}]},{"number":27,"translation":"And what can make you know what is Saqar?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"And what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","english":"can make you know","translit":"adrāka","root":"دري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَقَرُ","english":"(is) Hell","translit":"saqaru","root":""}]},{"number":28,"translation":"It lets nothing remain and leaves nothing [unburned],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُبْقِى","english":"it lets remain","translit":"tub'qī","root":"بقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَذَرُ","english":"it leaves","translit":"tadharu","root":"وذر"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"Blackening the skins.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَوَّاحَةٌۭ","english":"Scorching","translit":"lawwāḥatun","root":"لوح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْبَشَرِ","english":"the human (skin)","translit":"lil'bashari","root":"بشر"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"Over it are nineteen [angels].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","english":"Over it","translit":"ʿalayhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تِسْعَةَ","english":"(are) nine","translit":"tis'ʿata","root":"تسع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَشَرَ","english":"teen","translit":"ʿashara","root":"عشر"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"And We have not made the keepers of the Fire except angels. And We have not made their number except as a trial for those who disbelieve - that those who were given the Scripture will be convinced and those who have believed will increase in faith and those who were given the Scripture and the believers will not doubt and that those in whose hearts is hypocrisy and the disbelievers will say, \"What does Allah intend by this as an example?\" Thus does Allah leave astray whom He wills and guides whom He wills. And none knows the soldiers of yo